(283,1,'2026-04-08 21:42:45','2026-04-08 18:42:45','<h2>Election work</h2>\nUusimaa Greens coordinates election work in municipal, wellbeing services county and parliamentary elections. We also participate in the party\'s campaign in European and presidential elections.\n\nWe also provide election training for candidates and their supporters and supply campaign materials. Where possible, we support Green candidates in other elections too.\n<h2>Candidates</h2>\nThe party\'s candidate information will be published when the election campaign begins.\n<h2>Stand as a candidate</h2>\nInterested in running? We\'ll help you get started. <a href=\"/en/elections/stand-as-candidate/\">Read more</a>','Elections','','publish','closed','closed','','elections','','','2026-04-08 21:42:45','2026-04-08 18:42:45','',0,'http://localhost:8081/elections/',0,'page','',0),
