(287,1,'2026-04-08 21:42:45','2026-04-08 18:42:45','<p>This page publishes the register and privacy policy statements for the processing of personal data as referred to in the EU General Data Protection Regulation ((EU) 2016/679). These statements apply to the extent that Uudenmaan Vihreät ry is the data controller.</p>\n<p><strong>Registers:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1rxdvqOBwlci0NsitEKTfzxvFW0I3bOdGMU0itCPzKE0/edit?usp=sharing\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">register of elected officials</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1EGt9xFR3hL91K-KadTMUP5cApQLLz1zODkyfsiD0cu4/edit\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">candidate nomination register</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1U08CvmxDH7TKuVCY-qJ5R0VSFpRbvpykP4Vg_nKU92E/edit\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Uusimaa mailing list person register</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1GQDbKI-WmiymL4YJ7UZqAgKxy7-9_At6M5Brk6YlB0A/edit\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">media and stakeholder register</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>The data protection officer for Uudenmaan Vihreät ry is Executive Director Oskari Sundström. All data requests regarding the above registers should be sent to <a href=\"mailto:oskari.sundstrom@vihreat.fi\">oskari.sundstrom@vihreat.fi</a> with the subject line <em>Data request</em>.</p>\n<p>If the data concerns e.g. a membership, candidate or donor register, the data controller is <a href=\"https://www.vihreat.fi/tietosuoja\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Vihreä liitto rp</a>, and data requests should be addressed to them.</p>','Privacy policy','','publish','closed','closed','','privacy-policy','','','2026-04-08 21:42:45','2026-04-08 18:42:45','',0,'http://localhost:8081/privacy-policy/',0,'page','',0),
(288,1,'2026-04-08 21:42:45','2026-04-08 18:42:45','<h2>The district in brief</h2>\nThe district organisation\'s purpose is to promote <strong>green values</strong>: nature and environmental protection, sustainable development, social justice, equality, tolerance, openness and transparency in decision-making.\n\nUudenmaan Vihreät ry (founded 1984) is a member organisation of <a href=\"https://www.vihreat.fi/\">Vihreä liitto rp</a> and acts as the Green Party\'s district organisation in the <a href=\"https://fi.wikipedia.org/wiki/Uudenmaan_vaalipiiri\">Uusimaa electoral district</a>. In Helsinki, <a href=\"http://www.helsinginvihreat.fi/\">Helsinki Greens</a> operates. Uusimaa Greens\' purpose is to promote green values through its activities. To realise this, Uusimaa Greens primarily does election work, including nominating candidates for parliamentary elections and supporting its member associations in municipal elections.\n\nUusimaa Greens follows openness and impartiality in its operations.\n<h2>Governance &amp; documents</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1KzX4MnbQZMx8RZ8k97FQWTj265ZKYN0oqAMxs7maKQI/edit?usp=sharing\">District statutes</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/privacy-policy/\">Privacy policy</a></li>\n</ul>','About us','','publish','closed','closed','','about-us','','','2026-04-08 21:42:45','2026-04-08 18:42:45','',0,'http://localhost:8081/about-us/',0,'page','',0),
(289,1,'2026-04-08 21:42:45','2026-04-08 18:42:45','<h2>Uusimaa Greens\' <strong>extraordinary general meeting 1/2026</strong></h2>\n<b>Venue</b>: Green Party office, Mannerheimintie 15b, A staircase, 4th floor, 00260 Helsinki. The venue is accessible.\n\n<b>Time:</b> Saturday 11 April 2026 at 15:00. (Proxy verification at 14:00, day\'s programme begins at 10:30.)\n\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1cFhiNT9Gpj-bTnhI5-GHnh0p3MOhle-w/view?usp=sharing\">Meeting agenda</a>','General meeting','','publish','closed','closed','','general-meeting','','','2026-04-08 21:42:45','2026-04-08 18:42:45','',281,'http://localhost:8081/news/general-meeting/',0,'page','',0),
