(295,1,'2026-04-08 21:42:45','2026-04-08 18:42:45','<p>The Western Uusimaa wellbeing services county covers Espoo, Hanko, Inkoo, Karkkila, Kirkkonummi, Lohja, Raasepori, Siuntio and Vihti.</p>\n<h2>Greens in Western Uusimaa</h2>\n<p>Uusimaa Greens has active elected officials in the Western Uusimaa wellbeing services county. We work for better services, environmental protection and residents\' wellbeing.</p>\n<h2>Elected officials</h2>\n<p>[Names and contact details of elected officials here]</p>','Western Uusimaa','','publish','closed','closed','','western-uusimaa','','','2026-04-08 21:42:45','2026-04-08 18:42:45','',284,'http://localhost:8081/wellbeing-counties/western-uusimaa/',0,'page','',0),
(296,1,'2026-04-08 21:42:45','2026-04-08 18:42:45','<p>The Central Uusimaa wellbeing services county covers Hyvinkää, Järvenpää, Mäntsälä, Nurmijärvi, Pornainen, Sipoo and Tuusula.</p>\n<h2>Greens in Central Uusimaa</h2>\n<p>Uusimaa Greens has active elected officials in the Central Uusimaa wellbeing services county. We work for better services, environmental protection and residents\' wellbeing.</p>\n<h2>Elected officials</h2>\n<p>[Names and contact details of elected officials here]</p>','Central Uusimaa','','publish','closed','closed','','central-uusimaa','','','2026-04-08 21:42:45','2026-04-08 18:42:45','',284,'http://localhost:8081/wellbeing-counties/central-uusimaa/',0,'page','',0),
(297,1,'2026-04-08 21:42:45','2026-04-08 18:42:45','<p>The Eastern Uusimaa wellbeing services county covers Askola, Lapinjärvi, Loviisa, Myrskylä, Porvoo, Pukkila and Sipoo.</p>\n<h2>Greens in Eastern Uusimaa</h2>\n<p>Uusimaa Greens has active elected officials in the Eastern Uusimaa wellbeing services county. We work for better services, environmental protection and residents\' wellbeing.</p>\n<h2>Elected officials</h2>\n<p>[Names and contact details of elected officials here]</p>','Eastern Uusimaa','','publish','closed','closed','','eastern-uusimaa','','','2026-04-08 21:42:45','2026-04-08 18:42:45','',284,'http://localhost:8081/wellbeing-counties/eastern-uusimaa/',0,'page','',0),
(298,1,'2026-04-08 21:42:45','2026-04-08 18:42:45','<p>The Vantaa and Kerava wellbeing services county is responsible for social and health services in Vantaa and Kerava.</p>\n<h2>Greens in Vantaa–Kerava</h2>\n<p>Uusimaa Greens has active elected officials in the Vantaa–Kerava wellbeing services county. We work for better services, environmental protection and residents\' wellbeing.</p>\n<h2>Elected officials</h2>\n<p>[Names and contact details of elected officials here]</p>','Vantaa–Kerava','','publish','closed','closed','','vantaa-kerava-en','','','2026-04-08 21:42:45','2026-04-08 18:42:45','',284,'http://localhost:8081/wellbeing-counties/vantaa-kerava-en/',0,'page','',0),
